transcript.text: Hello! Welcome to our service center. I'm here to help you schedule your vehicle service. May I have your name please?
Hi, my name is Nick Patterson
Nice to meet you, Nick! And what's the best phone number to reach you at?
Perfect, thank you! Now, what vehicle are you bringing in for service today?
I have a 2020 Toyota Camry, silver color. It has about 45,000 miles on it.
Great! A 2020 Toyota Camry. What service do you need today?
I need an oil change and tire rotation. Also, my check engine light came on yesterday.
I understand. We'll do the oil change, tire rotation, and run a diagnostic for that check engine light. When would you like to bring it in?
How about this Friday morning, around 9am?
Friday at 9am works perfectly! I'll get you scheduled. Do you have your VIN number handy?

Perfect! I have you all set for Friday, October 20th at 9:00 AM for oil change, tire rotation, and check engine light diagnostic. We'll send you a confirmation email shortly. Is there anything else I can help you with today?
You're welcome, Nick! We look forward to seeing you and your Camry on Friday. Have a great day!
